Sou described how her experience was somewhat contradictory to the peace the
town usually offers:

> El 1ro de mayo fue a La Cumbrecita (Córdoba) y me decían que necesitaban un
> descanso por la cantidad de turistas que venían teniendo. 🌱🌱🌱
>
> — Sou🌱🌱🌱 (@sou_2014) [28 de mayo de
> 2017](https://twitter.com/sou_2014/status/868974890061377537)

> On May 1st [Labor Day in many countries], I went to La Cumbrecita (Córdoba),
> and there I was told they were already needing a break from all the tourists
> they were receiving.

Meanwhile, Aldana Martínez shared her bigger wish:

> Haría cualquier cosa con tal de mudarme a la Cumbrecita 😔😭.
>
> — Aldana Martinez (@aldi_lodigiani) [16 de mayo de
> 2017](https://twitter.com/aldi_lodigiani/status/864329922705317888)

> I'd do anything to move to La Cumbrecita.

